				services will be provided to these
				individuals.</text>
					</paragraph>
          <after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block>
        </quoted-block>
			</subsection>
      <subsection commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H41055B9BC9F1478BB15A65D3713045E7">
